s/architecture/picod.md` with:\n  - [ ] Local code execution daemon description (sidecar role)\n  - [ ] Workspace isolation and sanitization explanation\n  - [ ] File operations documentation (upload, download, list)\n  - [ ] Code execution timeout management\n  - [ ] Endpoint details: `/api/execute`, `/api/files`\n\n### Agentd Component\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/agentd.md` with:\n  - [ ] Controller-runtime architecture explanation\n  - [ ] Idle threshold detection logic\n  - [ ] Leader election for singleton controller\n  - [ ] Cleanup workflow steps\n  - [ ] Configuration parameters: `--idle-threshold`, `--check-interval`, `--leader-election`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Data Flow Documentation (REQ-003)\n\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow/` directory\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow/sandbox-creation.md` with:\n  - [ ] Step-by-step flow diagram: SDK → Router → WorkloadManager → K8s API → Router → SDK\n  - [ ] Timeout and retry behavior notes for each step\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow/code-execution.md` with:\n  - [ ] Execution flow: Client → Router → PicoD → Router → Client\n  - [ ] Error handling scenarios (timeout, sandbox not ready, invalid auth)\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow/session-routing.md` with:\n  - [ ] Session state maintenance explanation (Redis/Valkey mappings)\n  - [ ] Session key structure documentation (`session:<id>`)\n  - [ ] Session TTL and cleanup logic\n  - [ ] Session lifecycle states: Created, Active, Expired, Terminated\n\n---\n\n## Phase 4: Python SDK API Documentation (REQ-004)\n\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/api/sdk-python/` directory\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/api/sdk-python/overview.md` with:\n  - [ ] Installation instructions (`pip install agentcube-sdk`)\n  - [ ] Quick start code example\n  - [ ] SDK architecture diagram (Control Plane vs Data Plane)\n  - [ ] Version compatibility table\n- [ ] Create `docs/docs/api/sdk-python/code-interpreter-client.md` with:\n  - [ ] Cl